column4: Diversity (Global) – DIVG2 Change – Students will explain examples of how local to global cultures and societies change through convergence and/or divergence.
column11: Advanced: Demonstrate a sophisticated and multi-layered ability to explain examples of how local to global cultures and societies change through convergence and/or divergence.
column13: Proficient: Demonstrate an advanced ability to explain examples of how local to global cultures and societies change through convergence and/or divergence.
column15: Progressing: Demonstrate a basic ability to explain examples of  how local to global cultures and societies change through convergence and/or divergence.
column17: Beginning: Demonstrate a partial ability to explain examples of how local to global cultures and societies change through convergence and/or divergence.
column19: Unsatisfactory: Demonstrates little ability to explain examples of how local to global cultures and societies change through convergence and/or divergence.
